---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Bitora CRM: clienti, lead ed email integrate | Piemonte"
  description="Web app CRM professionale (Next.js + Supabase) per PMI, freelance e agenzie: gestione clienti ordinata, email integrate, licenze per utente, export CSV, SMTP personalizzato e API lead."
>
  <main class="bg-black text-white overflow-x-hidden selection:bg-indigo-500 selection:text-white">
    
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative h-screen flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center px-4">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_center,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-indigo-900/20 via-black to-black opacity-50"></div>
      
      <div class="relative z-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto space-y-8 opacity-0 animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s; animation-fill-mode: forwards;">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-indigo-400 backdrop-blur-md">
          Bitora CRM
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-8xl font-bold tracking-tight bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-white/60">
          Clienti, lead ed email.<br />
          Sotto controllo.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-400 font-light max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Bitora CRM è una web app professionale sviluppata in Next.js + Supabase per PMI, freelance e agenzie.
          <br class="hidden md:block" />
          Gestisci clienti e lead in modo ordinato, invia email dal CRM e mantieni controllo completo su accessi, licenze e dati.
        </p>
        <div class="pt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center items-center">
          <a href="/contattaci?topic=crm" class="min-w-[200px] px-8 py-4 bg-white text-black rounded-full font-medium text-lg transition-all hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(255,255,255,0.2)]">
            Richiedi una demo
          </a>
          <a href="#come-funziona" class="min-w-[200px] px-8 py-4 bg-white/10 text-white backdrop-blur-md rounded-full font-medium text-lg transition-all hover:bg-white/20 hover:scale-105">
            Vedi come funziona
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Intro / What it is -->
    <section id="come-funziona" class="py-32 px-6 md:px-12 border-t border-white/5">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-start">
          <div class="reveal-on-scroll">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 tracking-tight">Cos’è Bitora CRM</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
              Un CRM moderno, web-based e accessibile ovunque: nessuna installazione, nessun client da aggiornare, nessuna complessità inutile.
              È pensato per chi lavora con clienti reali e processi chiari, non per soluzioni enterprise sovradimensionate.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-white/10 rounded-3xl p-10 reveal-on-scroll" style="transition-delay: 100ms">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Valore pratico, ogni giorno</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-300">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                <span><span class="text-white font-medium">Controllo:</span> dati ordinati, pipeline leggibile, log email e export sempre disponibili.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                <span><span class="text-white font-medium">Semplicità:</span> interfaccia essenziale, campi utili, niente “feature” che complicano il lavoro.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                <span><span class="text-white font-medium">Automazione misurata:</span> tag e provenienza lead, template email e variabili dinamiche, deduplica per email.</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features Grid -->
    <section id="features" class="py-32 px-6 md:px-12 border-t border-white/5">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Feature 1 -->
          <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-white/10 p-10 rounded-3xl reveal-on-scroll group hover:border-indigo-500/50 transition-colors duration-500">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-500/20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-indigo-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4h-1M9 20H4v-2a4 4 0 014-4h1m8-4a4 4 0 10-8 0 4 4 0 008 0z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Clienti chiari e ordinati</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Crea clienti in pochi secondi, tieni contatti, note, tag e stato sempre sotto mano. Niente caos: solo dati utili.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-500">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-indigo-500"></div>
                Campi completi: contatti, note, tag, stato
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-indigo-500"></div>
                Pipeline semplice: nuovo → contattato → convertito → archiviato
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Feature 2 -->
          <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-white/10 p-10 rounded-3xl reveal-on-scroll group hover:border-purple-500/50 transition-colors duration-500" style="transition-delay: 100ms">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-500/20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 5H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v11a2 2 0 002 2h11a2 2 0 002-2v-5M18.5 2.5a2.121 2.121 0 013 3L12 15l-4 1 1-4 9.5-9.5z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Email integrate nel CRM</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Gestisci template, invii singoli e invii a gruppi selezionati senza strumenti esterni. Ogni invio è tracciato.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-500">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-purple-500"></div>
                Variabili dinamiche per messaggi personalizzati
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-purple-500"></div>
                Log invii: inviata / fallita / in coda
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Feature 3 -->
          <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-white/10 p-10 rounded-3xl reveal-on-scroll group hover:border-green-500/50 transition-colors duration-500" style="transition-delay: 200ms">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-500/20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-8 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 11c0-3.866 3.134-7 7-7 0 3.866-3.134 7-7 7zm0 0c0 3.866-3.134 7-7 7 0-3.866 3.134-7 7-7zm0 0v10"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Accesso, licenze, controllo</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Login sicuro e licenze per utente con trial automatico. Le funzionalità sono disponibili solo con licenza attiva.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-500">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-500"></div>
                Ideale per team piccoli e strutturati
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-500"></div>
                Controllo totale su utenti e permessi
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Detailed Sections -->
    <section class="py-32 px-6 md:px-12 border-t border-white/5">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-20 reveal-on-scroll">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 tracking-tight">Funzioni, spiegate con chiarezza</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 font-light max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            Ogni sezione è costruita per rendere il lavoro quotidiano più semplice: gestione clienti ordinata, comunicazioni tracciate e dati sempre disponibili.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-white/10 rounded-3xl p-10 reveal-on-scroll">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Gestione clienti chiara e ordinata</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Crea e aggiorna clienti rapidamente. Tutto ciò che serve è al posto giusto, con una pipeline semplice e leggibile.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-500">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-indigo-500"></div>Vista tabellare responsive per desktop e tablet</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-indigo-500"></div>Stato e tag per trovare subito ciò che conta</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-white/10 rounded-3xl p-10 reveal-on-scroll" style="transition-delay: 75ms">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Email integrate, senza strumenti esterni</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Hub email nel CRM: template riutilizzabili, invii mirati e log completo degli stati.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-500">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-purple-500"></div>Invio a singoli clienti o gruppi selezionati</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-purple-500"></div>Newsletter informativa in BCC</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-white/10 rounded-3xl p-10 reveal-on-scroll" style="transition-delay: 150ms">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Statistiche ed export</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
              I dati sono sempre disponibili e portabili. Quando serve, esporti i clienti in CSV in qualsiasi momento.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-500">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-500"></div>Export CSV immediato</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-500"></div>Trasparenza: i dati restano tuoi</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-white/10 rounded-3xl p-10 reveal-on-scroll" style="transition-delay: 225ms">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">SMTP personalizzato e brand coerente</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Usi il tuo provider email (Gmail, Aruba, Outlook o server dedicato). Nessun lock-in e credenziali cifrate lato server.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-500">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-indigo-500"></div>Invii dal tuo dominio e con il tuo stile</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-indigo-500"></div>Configurazione pensata per sicurezza e controllo</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-white/10 rounded-3xl p-10 reveal-on-scroll" style="transition-delay: 300ms">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Integrazione con siti e form esterni</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
              API dedicata per ricevere lead dal sito o da landing page. Niente duplicati: se l’email esiste già, si aggiorna il contatto.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-500">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-purple-500"></div>Tag automatici e tracciamento provenienza</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-purple-500"></div>Perfetto per campagne e acquisizione lead</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-white/10 rounded-3xl p-10 reveal-on-scroll" style="transition-delay: 375ms">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Accesso e licenze</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Login sicuro e licenze per utente con trial automatico. Le funzioni sono disponibili solo con licenza attiva: controllo totale e costi prevedibili.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-500">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-500"></div>Licenze scalabili per team piccoli</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-500"></div>Accesso alle funzioni solo con licenza attiva</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-white/10 rounded-3xl p-10 reveal-on-scroll" style="transition-delay: 450ms">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Area Admin</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Per chi gestisce più utenti o più account: controllo centralizzato su utenti, licenze e monitoraggio.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-500">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-indigo-500"></div>Gestione utenti e licenze</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-indigo-500"></div>Monitoraggio e gestione clienti</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Pricing -->
    <section id="pricing" class="py-32 px-6">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-24 reveal-on-scroll">
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 tracking-tight">Licenze per utente, controllo totale</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 font-light">Scegli in base al numero di utenti. Trial automatico e funzionalità disponibili solo con licenza attiva.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Plan: Utente -->
          <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-white/10 rounded-3xl p-10 reveal-on-scroll text-center">
            <div class="inline-block bg-white/10 text-white/80 px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-8">Piano Utente</div>

            <div class="flex items-baseline justify-center gap-2 mb-6">
              <span class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white">€19,99</span>
              <span class="text-lg text-gray-500">/utente/mese</span>
            </div>

            <p class="text-gray-400 mb-10 max-w-sm mx-auto">
              Per freelance e professionisti: un CRM completo, accessibile ovunque, con email integrate e dati sempre esportabili.
            </p>

            <div class="space-y-4 text-left max-w-sm mx-auto mb-10">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-300">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Email integrate + log invii
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-300">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Export CSV in qualsiasi momento
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-300">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                SMTP personalizzato (tuo provider)
              </div>
            </div>

            <a href="/contattaci?plan=crm-user" class="inline-block w-full px-8 py-4 bg-white text-black rounded-full font-medium text-lg transition-all hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(255,255,255,0.2)]">
              Attiva Piano Utente
            </a>
            <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-gray-500">Trial automatico • Disattivazione quando vuoi</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Plan: Fino a 5 utenti -->
          <div class="relative group reveal-on-scroll">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-indigo-600 to-purple-600 rounded-3xl opacity-20 blur-2xl group-hover:opacity-30 transition duration-1000"></div>
            <div class="relative bg-zinc-900 border border-white/10 rounded-3xl p-10 text-center">
              <div class="inline-block bg-indigo-500/20 text-indigo-300 px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-8">Fino a 5 utenti</div>

              <div class="flex items-baseline justify-center gap-2 mb-6">
                <span class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white">€49,99</span>
                <span class="text-lg text-gray-500">/mese</span>
              </div>

              <p class="text-gray-400 mb-10 max-w-sm mx-auto">
                Per piccoli team e agenzie: gestione condivisa di clienti e lead, con accessi controllati e flussi ordinati.
              </p>

              <div class="space-y-4 text-left max-w-sm mx-auto mb-10">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-300">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                  5 accessi inclusi
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-300">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                  Area Admin per utenti e licenze
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-300">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                  API lead + deduplica per email
                </div>
              </div>

              <a href="/contattaci?plan=crm-5" class="inline-block w-full px-8 py-4 bg-white text-black rounded-full font-medium text-lg transition-all hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(255,255,255,0.2)]">
                Attiva Piano Team
              </a>
              <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-gray-500">Trial automatico • Disattivazione quando vuoi</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Plan: Enterprise -->
          <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-white/10 rounded-3xl p-10 reveal-on-scroll text-center" style="transition-delay: 100ms">
            <div class="inline-block bg-white/10 text-white/80 px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-8">Enterprise</div>

            <div class="flex items-baseline justify-center gap-2 mb-6">
              <span class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white">Su contatto</span>
            </div>

            <p class="text-gray-400 mb-10 max-w-sm mx-auto">
              Per team più strutturati o esigenze specifiche: numero utenti personalizzato, setup dedicato e requisiti di integrazione.
            </p>

            <div class="space-y-4 text-left max-w-sm mx-auto mb-10">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-300">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Numero utenti e licenze su misura
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-300">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Integrazioni e flussi dedicati
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-300">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                Supporto e onboarding concordati
              </div>
            </div>

            <a href="/contattaci?topic=crm-enterprise" class="inline-block w-full px-8 py-4 bg-white text-black rounded-full font-medium text-lg transition-all hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(255,255,255,0.2)]">
              Contattaci
            </a>
            <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-gray-500">Preventivo e tempi in base alle esigenze</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <section class="py-32 px-6 border-t border-white/5">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-16 text-center">Domande frequenti</h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <details class="group bg-white/5 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl open:bg-white/10 transition-all duration-300">
            <summary class="flex justify-between items-center p-6 cursor-pointer list-none">
